<section>
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <div class="card">
        <p>HopeHelpers is a compassionate organization dedicated to bringing joy and encouragement to children in hospitals through heartfelt handwritten letters. We believe that even the smallest message of hope can brighten a child's day.</p>
    </div>

    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <div class="card">
        <ul>
            <li>Volunteers write letters filled with love, positivity, and support.</li>
            <li>We collect, review, and deliver these letters to kids in partner hospitals.</li>
            <li>Children receive messages that remind them they are strong, brave, and never alone.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>Get Involved</h2>
    <div class="card">
        <p>Join us in spreading hope! Whether you want to write letters, donate supplies, or help us expand, your support makes a difference.</p>
    </div>

